room_title: Escape room "Vegas Hangover" by Escape Room Fayetteville in Fayetteville
review: We did the Vegas Hangover room. Very challenging. Cool electronics. We escaped with little time to spare. So much fun. Super nice hint master. Loved it!

room_title: Escape room "Vegas Hangover" by Escape Room Fayetteville in Fayetteville
review: I’ve been to plenty of Escape rooms and Las Vegas Hangover was, by far, my favorite. Luke was such an awesome Clue Master who kept us involved when we were stumped. I will certainly be back for the other rooms in the near future.

room_title: Escape room "Vegas Hangover" by Escape Room Fayetteville in Fayetteville
review: We did “Vegas Hangover” and had a great time! This was our first time doing an escape room and Luke was awesome!! Highly recommend this place and definitely plan to go back.
